					<p>All Service Fees are based on integration of the Platform to the Customer's own service offering, unless otherwise agreed separately. An introduction to the Platform may be provided by GameLayer (in a manner determined by GameLayer from time-to-time) and support, as further specified herein, will be included within the Service Fee.</p>
					
